    <title>Hexo博客Next主题note标签</title>
    <link href="http://mostlai.github.io/2020/04/01/note-tag/"/>
    <id>http://mostlai.github.io/2020/04/01/note-tag/</id>
    <published>2020-04-01T06:50:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-04-02T00:02:33.099Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1></blockquote><p>在Hexo编写文本时，为了表述的更清晰明确，往往可以通过note标签插件来实现。Note标签通过在左侧使用图标和划线，实现提醒功能。这里我以Next主题为示例，介绍一下note标签的用法。</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="Note配置"><a href="#Note配置" class="headerlink" title="Note配置"></a>Note配置</h1><p>打开uesername.github.io\themes\next_config.yml文件</p><p>搜索note关键词，找到以下代码</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">note:</span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="built_in"> Note </span>tag style values:</span><br><span class="line">  #  -<span class="built_in"> simple </span>   bs-callout old alert style. Default.</span><br><span class="line">  #  - modern    bs-callout new (v2-v3) alert style.</span><br><span class="line">  #  - flat      flat callout style with background, like on Mozilla <span class="keyword">or</span> StackOverflow.</span><br><span class="line">  #  - disabled  <span class="builtin-name">disable</span> all CSS styles import of<span class="built_in"> note </span>tag.</span><br><span class="line">  style:<span class="built_in"> simple </span>#<span class="built_in"> simple </span>| modern | flat | disabled</span><br><span class="line">  icons: <span class="literal">true</span> # 是否显示图标</span><br><span class="line">  border_radius: 3 # 圆角半径</span><br><span class="line">  # Offset lighter of background <span class="keyword">in</span> % <span class="keyword">for</span> modern <span class="keyword">and</span> flat styles (modern: -12 | 12; flat: -18 | 6).</span><br><span class="line">  # Offset also applied <span class="keyword">to</span> label tag variables. This option can work with disabled<span class="built_in"> note </span>tag.</span><br><span class="line">  light_bg_offset: 0 # 默认背景减淡效果，以百分比计算</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Note用法"><a href="#Note用法" class="headerlink" title="Note用法"></a>Note用法</h1><p>Note标签包括default | primary | success | info | warning | danger，下面我进行举例说明。</p><hr><p>None：</p><figure class="highlight django"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name">note</span> %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span>标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">文字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name">endnote</span> %&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note "><p><b>标题</b><br>文字</p></div><hr><p>Default ：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%<span class="built_in"> note default </span>%&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># default风格</span></span><br><span class="line">文字</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note default"><h1 id="default风格"><a href="#default风格" class="headerlink" title="default风格"></a>default风格</h1><p>文字</p></div><hr><p>Primary ：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%<span class="built_in"> note </span>primary %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># primary风格</span></span><br><span class="line">文字</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note primary"><h1 id="primary风格"><a href="#primary风格" class="headerlink" title="primary风格"></a>primary风格</h1><p>文字</p></div><hr><p>success ：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%<span class="built_in"> note </span>success %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># success风格</span></span><br><span class="line">文字</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note success"><h1 id="success风格"><a href="#success风格" class="headerlink" title="success风格"></a>success风格</h1><p>文字</p></div><hr><p>Info ：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%<span class="built_in"> note </span><span class="builtin-name">info</span> %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># info风格</span></span><br><span class="line">文字</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note info"><h1 id="info风格"><a href="#info风格" class="headerlink" title="info风格"></a>info风格</h1><p>文字</p></div><hr><p>Warning ：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%<span class="built_in"> note </span><span class="builtin-name">warning</span> %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># warning风格</span></span><br><span class="line">文字</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note warning"><h1 id="warning风格"><a href="#warning风格" class="headerlink" title="warning风格"></a>warning风格</h1><p>文字</p></div><hr><p>Danger ：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%<span class="built_in"> note </span>danger %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># danger风格</span></span><br><span class="line">文字</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note danger"><h1 id="danger风格"><a href="#danger风格" class="headerlink" title="danger风格"></a>danger风格</h1><p>文字</p></div><hr><p>无图标 ：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%<span class="built_in"> note </span><span class="builtin-name">info</span> no-icon %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 无图标</span></span><br><span class="line">文字</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note info no-icon"><h1 id="无图标"><a href="#无图标" class="headerlink" title="无图标"></a>无图标</h1><p>文字</p></div><hr>]]></content>
    
